_Huf’al_ Active Participle for Regular Shorushim:
The [[{{_huf’al_ active participle}} form]] has the following conjugation pattern for [[regular shorushim]]:
|            | *Masculine* | *Feminine* |
| *Singular* | מֻבְדָּל <br> _muvdol_ <br> [he is] being separated | מֻבְדֶּלֶת <br> _muvdeles_ <br> [she is] being separated |
| *Plural*   | מֻבְדָּלִים <br> _muvdolim_ <br> [those men are] being separated | מֻבְדָּלוֹת <br> _muvdolos_ <br> [those women are] being separated |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎ב, ‎ד, and ל above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugations.
